creator: Amy Lowell
description:
LibriVox recording of Men, Women and Ghosts by Amy Lowell.
Read in English by Little Tee; Leonard Wilson; Shakira Searle; TND; Anusha Iyer; John Van Stan; David Lawrence; Geoffrey Frazier; nbvoices; Sieska; Julia Niedermaier; Beatrix Manos; Etel Buss; ToddHW
This is a collection of long poems and short stories by Amy Lowell. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (158MB)
